<img data-gif src="/S/L/I/H-S1-C3.png" alt="small business service"></div><h5>Small business.</h5><p>Get started in minutes. Add lines as your team grows. Powerful call handling features.</p></div><div class="col-sm-3"><div class="point-img"><img data-gif src="/S/L/I/H-S1-C4.png" alt="value affordable phone system"></div><h5>Value.</h5><p>Works on all your existing devices. Prices start at below $10/month.</p></div></div></div></div></section><section data-d-nid="3" class="whole-width-text text-center"><div class="container"><div class="row"><div class="col-md-8 col-md-offset-2 col-sm-10 col-sm-offset-1 col-xs-12 col-xs-offset-0"><h2>Hello, Line2</h2><h4>Why use Line2 as your business phone service? Just ask our customers.</h4></div></div></div></section><section data-d-nid="163" class="half-text-half-image-wrapper story-section"><div class="container"><div class="row"><div class="col-md-5 col-md-offset-6 static"><div class="copy-wrapper"><div class="story-container" data-modal-populate="" data-story-id="1"><h4>Two lines, one phone, and so much more.</h4><div class="inline-image-container"><img src="/s/L/I/Story1-img1.jpg" alt="real estate"></div><p>When I see a Line2 call pop up, I know it’s business — I can prepare myself, get somewhere quiet to answer it, and make sure I’m in a position to be professional. <span class="more-content">Other services that give you a number just forward the call to your mobile phone, but that doesn’t help you identify them as business calls. Line2 offers real business class features at a great price. I’m using it for group messaging and photos, to manage inside sales calls, and to track results from advertising spend.</span></p><p><a data-link-action="populate-modal-link" href="javascript:void(0);">Read more</a></p><div class="person-story"><img src="/s/L/I/Story1-img2.jpg" alt="real estate kevin markarin"><div class="person-name"><p>Kevin Markarin</p><p><em>Marker Real Estate</em></p><p>San Francisco, CA</p></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></section><section data-d-nid="62" class="hr-section"><div class="container"><div class="row"><div class="col-sm-offset-12 col-sm-offset-0 col-md-10 col-md-offset-1"><hr></div></div></div></section><section data-d-nid="164" class="half-text-half-image-wrapper left-text story-section"><div class="container"><div class="row"><div class="col-md-5 col-md-offset-1 static"><div class="copy-wrapper"><div class="story-container" data-modal-populate="" data-story-id="2"><h4>Keep in touch with your team, wherever they are.</h4><div class="inline-image-container"><img src="/s/L/I/Story2-img1.jpg" alt="recruiting second phone"></div><p>In recruiting, we need to move fast and stay close to candidates to get them into jobs, even when my team is out in the field. <span class="more-content">Line2 helps us do that by delivering any call or message to any device, wherever we are. Connectivity isn’t a problem either, because Line2 works across Wi-Fi, data, or cell phone coverage, so even out in the oil patches we stay connected. This solution just makes sense.</span></p><p><a data-link-action="populate-modal-link" href="javascript:void(0);">Read more</a></p><div class="person-story"><img src="/s/L/I/Story2-img2.jpg" alt="recruiting melissa mcelfish"><div class="person-name"><p>Melissa McElfish</p><p><em>Energy Recruiting Services</em></p><p>Coeur d'Alene, Idaho</p></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></section><section data-d-nid="62" class="hr-section"><div class="container"><div class="row"><div class="col-sm-offset-12 col-sm-offset-0 col-md-10 col-md-offset-1"><hr></div></div></div></section><section data-d-nid="165" class="half-text-half-image-wrapper story-section"><div class="container"><div class="row"><div class="col-md-5 col-md-offset-6 static"><div class="copy-wrapper"><div class="story-container" data-modal-populate="" data-story-id="3"><h4>Never miss a call or text.</h4><div class="inline-image-container"><img src="/s/L/I/Story3-img1.jpg" alt="baby sitting phone"></div><p>Running a busy baby-sitting service in Los Angeles requires me and my partner to be constantly available to clients. <span class="more-content">Line2 enables us to distribute calls and texts to multiple numbers simultaneously, so we never miss one. It also gives us group texting so we can quickly reach out to several of our sitters at once to check availability. Using the phones and tablets we already owned meant we were up and running on the service in minutes. Also, adding new numbers is a snap.</span></p><p><a data-link-action="populate-modal-link" href="javascript:void(0);">Read more</a></p><div class="person-story"><img src="/s/L/I/Story3-img2.jpg" alt="kimberly gurss babysitting phone"><div class="person-name"><p>Kimberly Gurss</p><p><em>WeeSitting Babysitting Service</em></p><p>Los Angeles, CA</p></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></section><section data-d-nid="62" class="hr-section"><div class="container"><div class="row"><div class="col-sm-offset-12 col-sm-offset-0 col-md-10 col-md-offset-1"><hr></div></div></div></section><section data-d-nid="35" class="whole-btn-text text-center higher-top-padding higher-bottom-padding"><div class="container"><div class="row"><div class="col-xs-12"><a class="btn" href="/plans">Get Started</a></div></div></div></section><section data-d-nid="91" class="whole-width-text text-center no-top-padding"><div class="container"><div class="row"><div class="col-xs-12"><p>Find the right <a href="/plans">business phone plan</a> and discover all the ways to utilize your <a href="/features/how-it-works">business phone number</a>.</p></div></div></div></section></article><footer><div class="container"><div class="row"><div class="hidden-xs hidden-sm col-md-2"><h6><a id="Footer-Logo" href="/"><span>Line2</span></a></h6></div><div class="col-xs-5 col-md-2"><h6>Company</h6><ul><li><a href="/about/about-line2" id="Ftr-about">About Us</a></li><li><a href="http://news.line2.com/" id="Ftr-nr">News &amp; Reviews</a></